	abstract = {In this study, we analyze a series of images of Io obtained with the 
European Southern Observatory adaptive optics system (Adaptive Optics
Near Infrared System, ADONIS) at 3.8 μm from 1996 to 1999, with
particular emphasis on the observations carried out in late 1999 in
